	<question id="2011BeijingGaokao_15_01" type="shortanswer">
		<text format="latex">因为$f(x)=4\cos x\sin(x+\frac{\pi}{6})-1=4\cos x(\frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}\sin x+\frac{1}{2}\cos x)-1=\sqrt{3}\sin2x+2\cos^2x-1=\sqrt{3}\sin2x+\cos2x=2\sin(2x+\frac{\pi}{6})$，所以$f(x)$的最小正周期为$\pi$.</text>
	</question>
	
	<question id="2011BeijingGaokao_15_02" type="shortanswer">
		<text format="latex">因为$-\frac{\pi}{6}\leq x\leq\frac{\pi}{4}$,所以$-\frac{\pi}{6}\leq 2x+\frac{\pi}{6}\leq\frac{2\pi}{3}$.于是,当$2x+\frac{\pi}{6}=\frac{\pi}{2}$,即$x=\frac{\pi}{6}$时,$f(x)$取最大值2;当$2x+\frac{\pi}{6}=-frac{\pi}{6}$时,即$x=-\frac{\pi}{6}$时,$f(x)$取得最小值-1.</text>
	</question>
	
