	<question id="2011BeijingGaokao_19_01" type="shortanswer">
	     <text format="latex">由已知得$c=2\sqrt{2}$,$\frac{c}{a}=\frac{\sqrt{6}}{3}$,解得$a=2\sqrt{3}$.又$b^{2}=a^{2}-c^{2}=4$.所以椭圆G的方程为$\frac{x^{2}}{12}+\frac{y^{2}}{4}=1$.</text>
	</question>
	
	<question id="2011BeijingGaokao_19_02" type="shortanswer">
	    <text>设直线l的方程为$y=x+m$.由
	    $$ \left\{
                   \begin{aligned}
                   y=x+m \\
                   \frac{x^{2}}{12}+\frac{y^{2}}{4}=1\\
                   \end{aligned}
                   \right.
        $$
		得$4x^{2}+6mx+3m^{2}-12=0$.设A,B的坐标分别为$(x_{1},y_{1})$,$(x_{2},y_{2})$($x_{1}＜x_{2}$),AB的中点为$E(x_{0},y_{0})$,则$x_{0}=\frac{x_{1}+x_{2}}{2}=-\frac{3m}{4}$,$y_{0}=x_{0}+m=\frac{m}{4}$.因为AB是等腰VPAB的底边,所以$PE\perp AB$.所以PE的斜率$k=\frac{2-\frac{m}{4}}{-3+\frac{3m}{4}}=-1$.解得$m=2$.此时方程$4x^{2}+6mx+3m^{2}-12=0$为$4x^{2}+12x=0$,解得$x_{1}=-3$,$x_{2}=0$.所以$y_{1}=-1$,$y_{2}=2$.所以$|AB|=3\sqrt{2}$.
		此时,点$P(-3,2)$到直线$AB:x-y+2=0$的距离$d=\frac{|-3-2+2|}{\sqrt{2}}=\frac{3\sqrt{2}}{2}$,所以$\triangle PAB$的面积$S=\frac{1}{2}|AB|\cdot d=\frac{9}{2}$.</text>
	</question>
	
